OL,3,CParc Prison worker arrested over
OL,4,Calleged smuggling of contraband into
OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FPolice have arrested an employee of
OL,8,Fcrisis-hit Parc Prison on suspicion of
OL,9,Fsmuggling contraband into the jail.
OL,11,FThe prison worker is the fourth person
OL,12,Fwithin two months to have been
OL,13,Farrested in connection with illicit
OL,14,Fitems or drugs brought into the
OL,15,FBridgend jail.
OL,17,FParc has seen nine sudden inmate
OL,18,Fdeaths since February 27 but none of
OL,19,Fthe arrests are in connection with the
OL,20,Finvestigation into those deaths.
