OL,7,FThe arrest of the Parc employee
OL,8,Fhappened on Tuesday, 14 May.
OL,10,FA South Wales Police spokesperson
OL,11,Fsaid: "Detectives from Tarian, the
OL,12,Fregional organised crime unit for
OL,13,Fsouthern Wales, investigating the
OL,14,Fsupply of drugs into the area have
OL,15,Fmade a further arrest. A 36-year-old
OL,16,Fman was arrested on suspicion of
OL,17,Fconveying contraband into a prison. He
OL,18,Fhas been bailed pending further
OL,19,Finquiries."
