OL,7,FIt comes after police arrested a 40-
OL,8,Fyear-old man from Birmingham and a 34-
OL,9,Fyear-old woman from Penylan in Cardiff
OL,10,Fon March 21 on suspicion of conspiracy
OL,11,Fto supply controlled drugs and money
OL,12,Flaundering. Both have been released
OL,13,Funder investigation.
OL,15,FIn March police also arrested a 34-
OL,16,Fyear-old man, from Penylan in Cardiff,
OL,17,Fon suspicion of being concerned in the
OL,18,Fsupply of controlled drugs. He is on
OL,19,Fconditional bail pending further
OL,20,Finquiries.
