OL,7,FA spokesman for G4S, the private
OL,8,Fsecurity giant which runs Parc, said:
OL,9,F"Following a joint operation with
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police we can confirm that
OL,11,Fan employee was arrested on May 14. We
OL,12,Fexpect the highest standards of
OL,13,Fconduct from our employees and if we
OL,14,Fsuspect any form of wrongdoing we will
OL,15,Ftake swift action. Where there is any
OL,16,Fsuspicion of illegal behaviour we will
OL,17,Falways share intelligence with the
OL,18,Fpolice and other agencies."
