OL,10,FYou Need To Know...
OL,12,FIt comes after prisons minister Edward
OL,13,FArgar and executive director of the
OL,14,Fprison and probation service in Wales,
OL,15,FIan Barrow, faced questions from MPs
OL,16,Fon Wednesday.
OL,18,FMr Argar rejected calls for the UK
OL,19,FGovernment to strip G4S' contract to
OL,20,Fmanage the jail, which he described as
OL,21,F"well-run".
