OL,7,FHe said four of the nine recent sudden
OL,8,Fdeaths are believed to be drug-
OL,9,Frelated, four are not, and one is
OL,10,F"potentially so".
OL,12,FTwo of the deaths, he said, are
OL,13,Fthought to be from natural causes.
OL,15,FMr Barrow disagreed with claims that
OL,16,Fthe "vast majority" of the drugs in
OL,17,FParc are brought in by staff.
